The III. Path or The Third Path (Ger: Der III. Weg, Der Dritte Weg) is a minor German neo-Nazi political party. It was founded on September 28, 2013 by former NPD officials, and activists from the proscribed FNS. They have ties with Assad's government in Syria, Hezbollah in Lebanon, and the Nordic Resistance Movement in the Nordic countries. Their founder and chairman is Klaus Armstroff. The party mostly operates in Thuringia, Bavaria and Brandenburg.
